{"tid":111451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"話後生妹幾正嘅唔該收皮 因為你根本唔識食","createTime":"2017-02-07T12:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T03:03:56.000Z","uid":5044,"like":54,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b557ca8d77b68d6ed77f7f2dc8a2c0c77cc53d24","tid":111451,"uid":5044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"其實女人就好似一隻雞蛋咁<br />\n烚蛋就係後生妹 <br />\n摸落去係幾滑<br />\n但係食落就淡已無味<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以一個男人應該食嘅<br />\n係滷水蛋<br />\n或者你睇落去個蛋殼係裂嘅 又皺皮咁<br />\n但係當你剝開隻蛋<br />\nd黑水嘅滷水汁滲哂入隻蛋到<br />\n你就會不停咁啜隻蛋<br />\n將每一滴滷水汁啜哂出黎<br />\n就好似甘露一樣滋潤你嘅喉嚨<br />\n然後咬落去 你先發現 <br />\n滷水蛋真係有味好多<br />\n<br />\n所以呢排成日見到呢個後生妹話幾白滑我真係笑而不語<br />\n因為你根本唔識食女人"},{"pid":"867484f1649daaa80a5f6d3a0104a6072c25b002","tid":111451,"uid":5044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210d22ff01a4f791b45407a710e68d5c91424d4c","tid":111451,"uid":5044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e41a40da1a5b921fe986deb3062f9cdbd39013","tid":111451,"uid":5044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6ad611015d1f0af1ee8fb244de22d92e53f6e4","tid":111451,"uid":353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"8412895a72811d91c1d168fbb91730382c49c5f6","tid":111451,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"032e71eb469bd7a0fd921749b0c89271afe1951e","tid":111451,"uid":11914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T12:04:56.000Z","msg":"想做潮文冇咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb742f17023aad43ff9bf879ca5dba82a